30... Kh7 31. h4 Qd1 32. Be2 Qe1 33. h5 { Creating a cage for the Black King. }
33... d4 { A desperate try to get some activity. } 34. c4
{ Taking the d5-square under control and avoiding any nonsense. White is completely winning. }
34... c5 35. Qf5+ Kg8 36. Qc8+ Kh7 37. Bf3
